Sentencas: In this research, solid oxide fuel cell electrolytes were fabricated by aqueous tape-casting technique.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting

Sentencas: The basic compositions for SOFC electrolyte systems were focused on yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) system.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting

Sentencas: The powders used in this study were from different sources.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting

Sentencas: ZrO2-based system doped with 3, 8, and 10 mol% of Y2O3, and 8YSZ electrolyte tape illustrated the desirable properties.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting

Sentencas: The grain size of the sintered electrolyte tapes was in the range of 0.5-1 mu m with 98-99% of theoretical density.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting

Sentencas: Phase and crystal structure showed the pure cubic fluorite structure for 8-10 mol% YSZ and tetragonal phase for 3 mol% doped.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting

Sentencas: The electrolyte tapes sintered at 1450 degrees C for 4 h had the highest ionic conductivity of 30.11 x 10(-3) S/cm which was measured at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting

Sentencas: The flexural strengths were in the range of 100-180 MPa for 8-10 mol% YSZ, and 400-680 MPa for 3 mol% YSZ.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte materials for solid oxide fuel cells by tape-casting
